project.name: Vaken
project.description: Vaken is a hackathon management system featuring hacker registration, applications, NFC, event management, and sponsor management developed by VandyHacks, the hackathon organization at Vanderbilt University. Vaken is our primary open-source project, and we also open-source our websites, internal tools, and pedagogical workshops we teach at hackathons.

applicant.name: Gabriel Ting
applicant.role: Previous President of VandyHacks, currently advisor and developer
